	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You're running the PAL version of Battletoads in NTSC emulation mode - when I tried this in Nintendulator, I saw the exact same thing.
<br />
<br />Solution: either switch your emulator to PAL, or get the NTSC ROM image.

		

		</td>
